high_descs: Turn left and go to the cabinet above the coffee maker
Open the cabinet and take out the glass vase and close the doors
Turn right then left back to the cabinet
Open the cabinet above the coffee maker
Put the vase on top of the plate and take them both from the cabinet
Turn left and walk to the sink on the left
Put the glass and plate in the sink to the left of the lettuce
anns.task_desc: Put a vase and plate from a cabinet into the sink

high_descs: Walk across the room, then turn left and walk across the room.
Look above the coffee maker and open the cabinet to take the glass jar.
Turn to the right and take one step, then turn left and look above the coffee maker.
Put the glass jar in the cabinet on top of the plate.
Take the plate with the jar on it out of the cupboard.
Turn left and take two steps, then turn left.
Place the plate and jar in the sink to the right of the lettuce.
anns.task_desc: To put the plate and jar in the sink.

high_descs: Walk to the wall then turn left and walk to the coffee maker and then take a small step left.
Get the glass bottle from the cupboard above the coffee maker then close the doors.
Take a small step to your right.
Put the bottle on the plate in the cupboard above the coffee maker.
Pick up the plate with the bottle on it and close the cupboard doors..
Turn left and walk to the sink and face it.
Put the plate in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a plate with a bottle on it in the sink.
